<TEI.2><text><body><div1 type="alphabetic letter" n="U" org="uniform" sample="complete"><entryFree key="Unlock" type="main" opt="n"><orth extent="full" opt="n">Unlock,</orth> 1) to open what is shut with a lock; properly and figuratively: <bibl n="shak. luc 16" default="NO" valid="yes">Lucr. 16</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. lll 1.1.109" default="NO" valid="yes">LLL I, 1, 109</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 1.1.139" default="NO" valid="yes">Merch. I, 1, 139</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mv 2.9.52" default="NO" valid="yes">II, 9, 52</bibl>. <bibl n="shak. mac 5.1.6" default="NO" valid="yes">Mcb. V, 1, 6</bibl>.<lb />2) to unfasten in general, to loose: <cit><quote>I'll frush it and u. the rivets all,</quote> <bibl n="shak. tro 5.6.29" default="NO" valid="yes">Troil. V, 6, 29</bibl></cit>.
</entryFree></div1></body></text></TEI.2>